summary: BTS written ship request☺️ Heyy can I have a written ship pls ☺️ I‘m german and thai, 5,6 ft tall (168cm), skinny but with...
body:
BTS written ship request☺️

Heyy can I have a written ship pls ☺️ I‘m german and thai, 5,6 ft tall (168cm), skinny but with feminine curves, brown green eyes and long hair (And yep that on my Profilepic is me😋) I‘m a funny person so i love to laugh and make people laugh, a bit crazy and loud but I have my moods sometimes where I want to be alone or just want to cuddle. I‘m very caring and loving if someone I care about isn‘t feelin good. Things I love are: Netflix,Dogs,Music,Singing and Photography.Thank you in advance❤️

Hai 🌸 @yourfavouritnightmare I ship you with Taehyung!

First of all you’re really beautiful! Okay now I think you would make an aestheticly pleasing couple, you guys look good together in my opinion. But it’s not just that, you seem to have a quite bubbly personality just like him. You guys would have so much fun together. From aside you might look like a crazy or sometimes childish couple, but the thing is I think you’d make people jealous of your relationship with how happy you both are in each other’s company. Taehyung might seem like this crazy clueless baby most of the time but I think he’s very mature behind closed doors. So he would always be respectful when you wanna be left alone and would try to help when you’re not feeling the best. You guys would be very loving and caring towards each other, also he’s the biggest cuddler in bts according to me so he would often fall asleep in your arms. He would love it when you share your interests with him and would be more than happy to do them with you. I can also see you guys expanding your family by adding a dog or two or maybe more who knows. Overall I think he’s a great match for you and I hope you agree.

Thank you for requesting! 💓

title: ONESHOT Requests!
body:
Okay, so due to the fact that I did not celebrate my 2K+ (almost at 2.2k now lol) followers appropriately, I will be giving away 2 One Shots to my readers.

I will choose two prompts / requests from the submissions.

All you have to do is send me either a prompt, dialogue, or song that you want a one-shot based on; along with the member and which group they belong to.

The winners will be chosen this weekend, and I will announce it via a post. Anon submissions are welcome.

I will also be doing an Album giveaway for my birthday (I will let you all know more details later).

caption:
I just want to reblog this and stress this: RM lost his entire band. He didn’t lose 20% of his band. He didn’t even lose 50%. He lost his whole band. Look at what it’s done to him. You can see the death in his eyes, but he keeps on going. This is why RM is one of my favorite idols.
